Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:18.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She's an angel! It's like\Nan angel is riding a horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.80,0:00:22.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen\Nsuch a beautiful lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:24.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I wish I were that horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.51,0:00:27.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the horse's rear legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:30.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Angel?! If she had wings...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.62,0:00:32.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...she wouldn't have\Nto ride on the horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.56,0:00:34.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,They're so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:36.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Rear legs? Is he talking about\Na two-man horse in a play?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:39.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What about a two-man\Nhorse in a play?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:41.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's stupid boy-talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.88,0:00:43.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,They're talking about\Nthe princess of their dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.28,0:00:47.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,On their way to school\Nthere's a mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:51.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,In the large yard, a lady\Nwho gracefully rides a horse...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.93,0:00:54.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...is the Madonna\Nthat the boys are admiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:00:58.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,They sneak by to watch her\Nevery day on their way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.34,0:00:59.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How perverted!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.81,0:01:01.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.15,0:01:04.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Asuka Jr.\Ngoes there, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.19,0:01:07.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Is she that pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:10.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?! You haven't seen her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:11.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,- No.\N- Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:13.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I can take you there today!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.37,0:01:15.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.18,0:01:17.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm not that interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:20.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Man! Asuka's head is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:23.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...filled only with\Nthoughts of St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.40,0:01:34.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,RETURN THE THOROUGHBRED!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.37,0:01:50.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.47,0:02:09.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?! She was cheated\Nand lost the horse...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:11.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...that the boys\Nwere talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:14.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The horse's name is Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:18.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Both Billy's father and mother\Nwere very famous racehorses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:21.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He's a top-notch Thoroughbred.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:24.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But that Madonna, rather,\NMs. Maki Nishina was against...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:26.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...turning him into a racehorse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.51,0:02:27.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,So he became a riding horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:35.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's a very extravagant\Nthing to do, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.93,0:02:39.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If he's so famous,\Nhe's worth quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:41.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Like they say, she must be\Nan extremely rich princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.90,0:02:44.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes. And according\Nto some people...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:47.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...she's wasting a fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.38,0:02:50.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,A man named Soma\Nkept visiting Maki's house...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:53.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...asking her to sell Billy to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:02:58.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But Maki flatly refused his offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:03:00.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But Soma wouldn't\Ngive up, and one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:22.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Well, hello, Lady Maki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:24.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I won't sell Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:25.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many\Ntimes you come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:26.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...the answer remains the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:28.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Now, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:33.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I've got a wonderful idea\Nthat may appeal to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:36.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,First, please look at this horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:40.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He's Wild Bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He's from a very\Nfamous bloodline.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.52,0:03:48.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He is as good as your Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:54.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This horse isn't\Na bad trade for Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:57.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:03:59.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I love Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:02.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll never give him\Nto someone like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:15.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:17.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.85,0:04:19.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:25.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?\NHis leg is broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:32.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The medical report\NSoma brought definitely stated...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:35.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...that the leg\Nwas broken, Maki said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:37.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that a broken leg is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:40.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...the same as\Na death sentence for a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:43.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's why Soma\Ndemanded Billy in exchange...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:47.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...as if he had\Nthe right to take Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:52.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She said her father\Ncouldn't refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:54.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But something is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:57.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Things were\Ntoo convenient for Soma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:05:00.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Only Soma is winning here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:02.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You mean...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:05.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Maki is thinking that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:08.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She thinks they were\Nset up from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:10.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Soma wanted Billy very badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:13.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And the horse's\Nbroken leg was supported...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.13,0:05:15.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...only by the medical report.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:19.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He tricked them\Nin order to get Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:23.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He had no intention\Nof giving up his horse, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:25.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Maki thinks so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:29.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She thinks they\Nsomehow surprised Billy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:31.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...and made him\Nfall into that horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:33.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes! That must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:39.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But Soma has already\Nbecome the legal owner of Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:42.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Billy and Maki\Nwill never be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:44.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:46.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Under such circumstances,\NSt. Tail can get the horse back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:50.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,In addition, I'll reveal\NSoma's evil intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:53.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But Billy is already scheduled...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:56.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...to go to a ranch\Nin Hokkaido tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:58.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And by train!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:05:59.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Train?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.28,0:06:03.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's the K-Express,\Nleaving Seika Station at 8:02.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:05.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We have only four hours\Nuntil its departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:06.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Please hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.55,0:06:20.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What short notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:22.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Did he go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:24.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How can I send him\Na warning note?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:26.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, have you seen Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:28.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:30.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Didn't he go home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:32.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Really? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:36.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There is no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:38.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It may be a bit much, but I guess\NI should use that method.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:52.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.25,0:06:54.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...I'll get Billy\Nfrom the K-Express train...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:56.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...leaving Seika Station at 8:02.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.32,0:06:59.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:00.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's a warning note...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:03.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's elaborate...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:05.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Dad! Let me borrow\Nyour train schedule!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:07.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The one you always\Nuse for your trips.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:09.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:12.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:13.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:18.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But why do you need it, Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:20.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Well... for something...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:25.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:26.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,- Mom!\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:28.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Is Meimi going on a trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:29.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Not that I know of.\NI haven't heard anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:33.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's running away...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:38.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If so, she wouldn't borrow\Nthe schedule from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:40.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:44.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of things\Ngoing on at her age.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:48.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's a difficult age...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:56.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...\Nthe K-Express departs at 8:02...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:59.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It will pass that point at...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:02.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:05.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,SEIKA STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:36.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:39.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail is coming to steal Billy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:41.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:44.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We'll be aboard the train\Nto protect the horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:45.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:49.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Here comes the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:05.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:12.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:15.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:20.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.56,0:09:38.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,May the blessings\Nof God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:59.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There are no suspicious\Npersons on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:00.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:03.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Position yourselves\Nat each place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:06.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,No! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:08.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Please let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:10.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's the commotion,\NMr. Soma?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:15.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Well, this young lady\Nwas doing a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:18.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She was trying to open\Nthe door of the livestock car...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:20.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...and let Billy escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:27.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I beg you! Please return Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:30.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're going too far, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:32.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Billy is mine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:35.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You don't have the right\Nto even touch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:37.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:39.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I know you set us up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:41.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There was no way Billy\Nwould get upset like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:42.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You made him upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.42,0:10:44.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He made Billy upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:46.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.69,0:10:48.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't say something\Nso stupid without any evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:50.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Never come close to this horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:53.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:57.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Who on earth are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:00.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Billy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:17.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Billy! Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:20.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:24.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.93,0:11:25.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:27.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:31.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.23,0:11:42.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:47.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Billy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.01,0:11:51.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:11:59.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I see. I understand the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:02.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm not doing anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:06.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that girl\Ncan't let go of Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:12.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But St. Tail always has\Na good reason for stealing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:16.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Rather than worrying about that,\Nhow about your security?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:19.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Even that girl\Nwas able to get close.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:21.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:23.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We have one officer on each car...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:27.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...and two officers\Nin front of the livestock car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:30.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I 'II be at the livestock car, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:32.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,So it's impossible to break in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:34.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:12:59.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,First, check the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:13.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That must be Soma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.57,0:13:15.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what they're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:19.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Darn! Why is Billy singled out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:21.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail wants him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:24.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That means Billy\Nis a very good horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:28.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Of course he is!\NThat's the reason I fell in love with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:31.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He'll bring us a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:33.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But that was a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:36.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You invented\NWild Bunch's broken leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:39.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You blamed it on Billy,\Nand then you got him for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:45.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The key was to use the fact\Nthat the girl didn't want to sell him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:48.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...coupled with your special talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:06.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's like we thought.\NThat's how they did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:09.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Now that we know,\NI'll take Billy no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:18.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The livestock car\Nis the very last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:21.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, Asuka Jr. is\Nkeeping it under surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.57,0:14:22.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:28.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How's it going?\NIs there anything unusual?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:30.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,No. Nothing so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:31.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:48.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is Asuka! I've found St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:50.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Get up on the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:55.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:58.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I was checking it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:00.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...and there's no officer\Nin the next car or anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:02.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:03.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:05.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What happened\Nto the kid, Asuka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.68,0:15:06.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I didn't see him, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.08,0:15:08.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Maybe something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:11.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:12.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:13.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:17.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't move, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:21.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Give up now!\NThere's nowhere to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:32.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.\NIsn't it strange that St. Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:36.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...shows up in the front\Nwhen Billy is in the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:44.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:48.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...Show...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:52.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:15.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Shoot! Someone's on the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:24.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Like we thought, it's St. Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:26.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:29.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ignore him! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:43.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:45.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Get off of me! Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:46.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.85,0:16:50.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:52.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:09.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:20.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.34,0:17:22.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:25.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:36.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She was all right...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:43.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What a stunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:45.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely catch you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:52.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you see\Nyour lady pretty soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:55.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Billy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:12.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:16.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:18.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.78,0:18:38.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.42,0:18:42.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...that Soma's wrong-doing\Nwas revealed to the police, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:46.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,So Billy is formally\Nreturned to Maki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:49.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:51.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But it's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:52.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He made up the story\Nabout the broken leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:54.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...and faked the medical report...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:57.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...and he upset Billy\Nby hitting him with a BB.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.59,0:18:59.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Really! I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:03.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Maki is riding Billy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:05.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She looked very cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:07.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The boys shouldn't\Nbe the only ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:08.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...to view her as an angel.
